release_note: Fixed purchase bug Previously: Hi Thinkers! With this update we re proud to bring you WRITING PROMPTS! You ll see them at the top when you write your entry. You can choose to use it or not and you can even change it if you want a new one! Research has shown writing prompts to be an effective tool to improving one s mental health and that s what we re all about! We hope you like it. Let us know what you think in the reviews or at support thinksmartjournal.com!
